title: BRIEF-Infineon invests nearly $300 mln in Wuxi new factory
text:
BRIEF-Infineon invests nearly $300 mln in Wuxi new factory 
Oct 8 Infineon Technologies AG 
* Builds a new factory in Wuxi, China 
* Says new factory is scheduled for rollout at the end of 2016, comprises total investment of nearly $300 million Source text: here Further company coverage: Trending On Reuters
